title: HUMAN EVENTS DAILY: NOV 5 2021 - FIONA HILL IMPLICATED IN LATEST DURHAM RELEASE.
description:
On today’s episode, Jack gives you the latest information regarding Kyle Rittenhouse, and the Steele Dossier. Fiona Hill is implicated in the latest Durham release, Durham is investigating the Brookings Institute, Daily Caller's reporting effectively ends the Kyle Rittenhouse case, and an eyewitness testifies that Rosenbaum threatened to kill Kyle Rittenhouse.   



Here’s your Daily dose of Human Events with @JackPosobiec
